ssh-vpn-gui (0.1.6) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix no connectivity to raw IP addresses (ping/TCP) over the tunnel.
    Marked traffic left tun3 with the LAN source address and was dropped by
    the remote masquerade; add a local SNAT to the tunnel address on tun3
    egress so fwmark-routed traffic is masqueraded correctly.

